[gd_scene format=3 uid="uid://b4w1y4ohvwki1"]

; Tutorial 03 - extend-lock bridge (option 1: one travel-bar, vertical reorient).
; FIRST PASS for feel. Layout is 3 deep (z=0,1,2), travel +x. Beats, left to right:
;   x=0      start (cube)
;   x=2..4   LockZone, form a (3,1,1) travel-bar and lock
;   x=6..8   1-wide bridge (z=1 only) - stay on the line, void both sides
;   x=11     1-cell gap - lie the bar across it (length)
;   x=14     Gate (open while locked) - pass through committed
;   x=15..17 UnlockZone, re-seat the (3,1,1) bar to release
;   x=18..20 1-wide corner - collapse to 1x1x1 to make the turn to the exit
;   x=20,z=2 End
; No perimeter walls: falling off the sides/gap is a restart, on purpose.

